---
// About 组件 - 个人简介
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
      <span class="text-primary-400">关于</span>我
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <!-- 左侧：简介文字 -->
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          你好！我是<strong class="text-white">如从</strong>，一名热爱技术的开发者。
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          我专注于前端开发和用户体验设计，善于将复杂的技术问题转化为简洁优雅的解决方案。
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          在工作中，我追求代码质量和工程效率的平衡，相信好的产品源于对细节的执着追求。
        </p>
        
        <!-- 快速信息 -->
        <div class="pt-4 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-400">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>中国</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-400">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span>前端开发 / 全栈开发</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 右侧：统计卡片 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-dark-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-dark-700 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-1">3+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">年开发经验</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-dark-700 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-1">10+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">完成项目</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-dark-700 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-1">5+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">技术栈</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-dark-700 hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-400 mb-1">∞</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">学习热情</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
